data.description: Now's your chance to own a CLASSIC Victorian Manor in prestigious College Hill! This EXPANSIVE estate consists of up to 9 Bedrooms & over 6,300 sq ft on a .40 acre corner lot. The main home consists of 5-6 BRs & 2.5 bathrooms on the 1st & 2nd floors,  as well as another 2-3 BR in-law suite or apartment on the 3rd floor with its own separate entrance. The main home boasts charm & character, HW floors, original wood trim accents & more! The beautiful wrap-around porch leads into a vestibule entrance & Foyer with a wood fireplace. Multiple living rooms, a den, kitchen, dining room & breakfast nook, and a 1/2 bath complete the 1st floor. Dual stairways lead you to the 6 graciously sized BRs & 2 full bathrooms. The 3rd Floor has refinished HW floors, its own living room & kitchen, bathroom additional BRs w/ large closets. This extra space is currently leased, producing over $20,000 in annual income! All this with a 2-car garage and circular driveway.
